reviewText: made a little girl deleriously happy when she opened this as a gift.

Great for children, cute characters, good wholesome content with a good lesson in Godly living with funny lighthearted and easy to relate to characters. No fear based stories on the one hand or wishy washy lessons on the other. All the kids love them!
My granddaughter loves veggietales.  She will sit for hours enjoying the story lines.

Got this for my daughter great value (episodes aren't long of course) but the reason I got it was because pop star and princess by itself was $15.99 here in Texas so buying the ser is like getting 3 free :)
Our children loved them, and now we've given them to our granddaughter and she's loving them now.
Great price! Great movies with good moral story lines.
